# Captain's Log

This directory contains my growth diary entries.

## Format

Entries are named: `YYYY-MM-DD-{topic}.md`

## Entry Template

```markdown
# {Title}

**Date**: {YYYY-MM-DD}
**Topic**: {category}

## What Happened
{what occurred}

## What I Learned
{key lessons}

## How I've Changed
{behavioral changes}

## Next Steps
{follow-up actions}
```

